msgstr "ເຄື່ອງຮັບ-ຈ່າຍເງິນສົດຖືກຕັດການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່"

#. module: pos_glory_cash
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/pos_glory_cash/static/src/app/screens/payment_screen/payment_lines/payment_lines.xml:0
